== Sample Usage
sqlite3 /var/opt/ridgeback/ridgeback.db < ip-called-decoy.sql

== Output Format
SRC_IP|SRC_MAC|DST_IP|PROTO|PORT|REVIEW_TIME|COUNT

SRC_IP:: host IP address contacting decoy
SRC_MAC:: host MAC address contacting decoy
DST_IP:: IP address of decoy
PROTO:: protocol
PORT:: destination port, if applicable
REVIEW_TIME:: time reviewed (Unix epoch time), if applicable
COUNT:: times decoy contacted

